channel.title: Bitwig 8-Track license up for grabs (GONE)
channel.description:
Anyone interested in a license for Bitwig 8-Track? It won't accept any kind of export (other than midi and stems) from Auxy, not as nicely as Live does anyway, but if anyone was interested in checking out a cross platform desktop DAW I have a license I won't be using. No charge, obviously.
Read more about it here https://www.bitwig.com/8-track.
Send me a msg please, first come first served. Thx.
